You can simply speak to Alexa to control your “Vactidy”. Following a few simple steps to connect Alexa with your products:
(1). Download the “Vactidy” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure your devices in our “Vactidy” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “Vactidy” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “Vactidy” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Vactidy” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup are completed. You can enjoy the voice control on your smart devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on T6 .”
“Alexa, turn off T6 .”
